data.description: Smith Douglas Homes proudly presents The Caldwell plan at Duncan's Crossing.  This owner-suite downstairs home boasts upgraded 36" kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, tile backsplash and luxury vinyl plan flooring in all main areas.  Added windows and covered rear patio also included!  Upstairs there's a huge loft/bonus room and 2 large 12x12 bedrooms and of course another full bathroom.  Home is in heart of cul-de-sac and backs to trees for a really nice natural privacy buffer!
